title: (Public Domain)Johnny_Dollar-The_Phantom_Chase_Matter-merged.mp3
description:
This is a merged version of the Your Truly Johnny Dollar episode titled "The Phantom Chase Matter." Total audio length is about 1 hour 50 minutes.

It was the second to last of the serialized Johnny Dollar adventures. It was also the longest, with 9 parts.

This merged version takes out the intro and ending stuff that has nothing to do with the story itself, so the whole adventure plays without interruption.

I used as the source the files provided onby the otrr (Old Time Radio Researchers) group, along with their permission
